##Ruby wrapper and command shell for the New York Times Congress API
## Limited to members, bio,roles, vote,positions, vote comparison,
## new members, current member states/district, missing vores, bills by member
##
## No nomination votes, bills cosponsers, recents bills, bill details, etc
